```
Generate a new blog post for the Freshwater Fishing Adventures category.

Title format: "Freshwater Fishing Expedition Photography & Videography in [Location] – [Year] Case Study"

Requirements:
- Create file: src/pages/blog/[kebab-case-title].jsx
- Add route in src/main.jsx
- Add entry to blogPosts array in src/pages/blog.jsx
- Include hero image, gallery images, and behind-the-scenes video
- Use category tag: "Freshwater Fishing Adventures"
- Include JSON-LD VideoObject structured data
- Follow the structure of freshwater-fishing-expedition-2025.jsx
- Include SEO meta tags with keyword aliases
- Publish date: [Month Day, Year]

Content should cover:
- Expedition objectives and context
